FBIS3-25668 "drafr037_c_94020" FBIS-AFR-94-037 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Feb 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA AVF Committee To Draw Up Homeland Constitution MB2402100794 Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network in English 0500 GMT 24 Feb 94 MB2402100794 Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The Afrikaner Volksfront's [Afrikaner National Front] transitional assembly has given its constitutional committee instructions to prepare a constitution for a volkstaat [homeland]. The president of the assembly, Dr. Ferdi Hartzenberg, said after a meeting in Pretoria that instructions had also been issued for a visual presentation of the boundaries of the proposed volkstaat.
